sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as Kiosk App
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>API: GET /api/v1/catalog [Met JWT Token]
    Note over API: Valideert JWT en checkt de rol

    alt Rol == Standaard Gebruiker
        API->>DB: SELECT category_id, COUNT(asset_id) FROM assets WHERE asset_status = 'AVAILABLE' AND is_deleted = FALSE GROUP BY category_id
        DB-->>API: Gecategoriseerde pool (bijv. Laptops: 3)
        API-->>Client: 200 OK (Standaard weergave)
    else Rol == Admin
        Note over API,DB: Admin heeft 2 joins nodig voor de actuele status
        API->>DB: SELECT a.*, l.loan_status, u.first_name, u.last_name FROM assets a LEFT JOIN loans l ON a.asset_id = l.asset_id AND l.loan_status IN ('ACTIVE', 'RESERVED') LEFT JOIN users u ON l.user_id = u.user_id WHERE a.is_deleted = FALSE
        DB-->>API: Volledige lijst (Asset + Locker info + Eventuele Lener)
        API-->>Client: 200 OK (Beheerdersweergave)
    end